kept praying and

00:10:26.150 --> 00:10:26.160
saying,

00:10:26.160 --> 00:10:28.069
'Lord, save me, help

00:10:28.069 --> 00:10:28.079
me.'And

00:10:28.079 --> 00:10:29.829
he said, 'No, I'm waiting on God to

00:10:29.839 --> 00:10:31.829
