00:10:31.839 --> 00:10:33.750
like a helicopter or

00:10:33.760 --> 00:10:35.430
something, and tried to throw a lifeline

00:10:35.440 --> 00:10:37.269
down and help him, and he said, 'No, I'm

00:10:37.279 --> 00:10:40.069
waiting on God.'And then, sure enough,

00:10:40.079 --> 00:10:42.310
finally the flood rose high

00:10:42.320 --> 00:10:44.630
enough that he died. And then he

00:10:44.640 --> 00:10:46.230
