that You would save me, but

00:10:52.240 --> 00:10:55.110
You never did.'And God said, 'I

00:10:55.120 --> 00:10:57.750
tried to. I sent the lifeboat. I

00:10:57.760 --> 00:11:00.310
sent the rescue helicopter. I sent all

00:11:00.320 --> 00:11:02.310
those people along your path, and you

00:11:02.320 --> 00:11:03.990
just didn't accept the help.'Right.

00:11:03.990 --> 00:11:04.000
And

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:04.870
there

00:11:04.870 --> 00:11:04.880
are

00:11:04.880 --> 00:11:06.550
so many in the body of

00:11:06.560 --> 00:11:08.230
Christ who do exactly that.

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:10.310
They only want divine encounters.

00:11:10.310 --> 00:11:10.320
And

00:11:10.320 --> 00:11:12.150
we have family that are like

00:11:12.160 --> 00:11:14.150
that, and I

00:11:14.160 --> 00:11:15.670
understand where you're faced. They say, 'Well, I

00:11:15.680 --> 00:11:17.350
don't even take a Tylenol if I have a

00:11:17.360 --> 00:11:18.790
