00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:37.110
crack and bleed all winter long because

00:11:37.120 --> 00:11:38.630
he thought it was against the Bible to

00:11:38.640 --> 00:11:40.069
put lotion on his hands. I'm talking

00:11:40.079 --> 00:11:42.389
about spiritual bondage, to the point

00:11:42.399 --> 00:11:46.870
where my aunt got bit by a brown recluse

00:11:46.880 --> 00:11:50.389
