00:11:50.399 --> 00:11:52.230
to come and get my aunt from my

00:11:52.240 --> 00:11:53.670
grandparents to take her to the

00:11:53.680 --> 00:11:55.430
hospital. But by the time

00:11:55.440 --> 00:11:57.190
they took her and got her

00:11:57.200 --> 00:11:59.509
there, the brown recluse bite made her

00:11:59.519 --> 00:12:02.310
so sick that she

00:12:02.310 --> 00:12:02.320
became

00:12:02.320 --> 00:12:04.710
mentally

00:12:04.710 --> 00:12:04.720
handicapped

00:12:04.720 --> 00:12:07.509
and still is today, and still has massive

00:12:07.519 --> 00:12:09.910
