you directly,

00:12:21.200 --> 00:12:23.269
then it wasn't God at

00:12:23.279 --> 00:12:25.030
all; you're just going to die. You know

00:12:25.040 --> 00:12:27.110
what I'm saying? And so my aunt is still

00:12:27.120 --> 00:12:29.750
mentally

00:12:29.760 --> 00:12:32.310
handicapped today,

00:12:32.320 --> 00:12:35.509
right now, and still has

00:12:35.519 --> 00:12:37.190
repercussions from that

00:12:37.200 --> 00:12:40.069
decision. And it was the wrong decision.

00:12:40.079 --> 00:12:41.670
It was the wrong—I'll say it right

00:12:41.670 --> 00:12:41.680
now—it

00:12:41.680 --> 00:12:43.350
was a wrong decision. She suffered

00:12:43.360 --> 00:12:45.590
her whole life because of someone else's

00:12:45.590 --> 00:12:45.600
decision,

00:12:45.600 --> 00:12:49.030
and it was because of that brown

00:12:49.030 --> 00:12:49.040
recluse.

00:12:49.040 --> 00:12:50.790
Now, that may make some people really

00:12:50.800 --> 00:12:51.910
mad, but I'm telling you, that's how

00:12:51.920 --> 00:12:53.670
extreme people get with this. I've been

00:12:53.680 --> 00:12:55.430
on the wrong side of this and the right

00:12:55.440 --> 00:12:57.750
side of it, watching people, and I'm

00:12:57.760 --> 00:12:59.430
telling you, there gets to be some

00:12:59.440 --> 00:13:01.590
bondage coming up in here where people

00:13:01.600 --> 00:13:03.110
can't even live. They go, 'Well, I can't

00:13:03.110 --> 00:13:03.120
even...'and

00:13:03.120 --> 00:13:04.150
you're like,

00:13:04.160 --> 00:13:06.389
'There's a cure there.'I can tell you

00:13:06.399 --> 00:13:08.150
another one. There was another

00:13:08.160 --> 00:13:10.629
girl in that church who had

00:13:10.639 --> 00:13:12.949
