00:13:12.959 --> 00:13:14.710
wouldn't even get her help, and DHS had

00:13:14.720 --> 00:13:16.150
to come and get her

00:13:16.160 --> 00:13:18.230
because the people were just being flaky.

00:13:18.240 --> 00:13:18.870
Yeah,

00:13:18.880 --> 00:13:21.269
you can get to the point where you're so

00:13:21.279 --> 00:13:24.310
religious and so brainwashed by things

00:13:24.320 --> 00:13:25.750
that it's like whenever they

00:13:25.750 --> 00:13:25.760
deal

00:13:25.760 --> 00:13:27.110
with snakes and dance around, you

00:13:27.120 --> 00:13:28.470
know, 'I'll touch any deadly thing and it

00:13:28.480 --> 00:13:29.509
won't harm me,'and they're dancing around

00:13:29.519 --> 00:13:31.190
with cobras and vipers and

00:13:31.200 --> 00:13:32.150
everything, and they bite them and they

