00:13:37.040 --> 00:13:38.629
snake, or the copperhead, or whatever

00:13:38.639 --> 00:13:39.990
bit me, and I didn't go to the doctor to

00:13:40.000 --> 00:13:41.590
get it taken care of, so I died. But if

00:13:41.600 --> 00:13:43.110
it's meant for me to take up

00:13:43.120 --> 00:13:44.629
these serpents,'I'm telling people, there

00:13:44.639 --> 00:13:46.150
is life there. Those kind of

00:13:46.160 --> 00:13:47.829
people are out there. So, you just have

00:13:47.839 --> 00:13:49.990
to use wisdom in these last days is what

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:51.750
I'm trying to say. I'm not trying to

00:13:51.760 --> 00:13:53.990
condemn anybody that doesn't believe in

00:13:54.000 --> 00:13:56.710
modern science. I'm not trying to say

00:13:56.720 --> 00:13:58.710
