00:14:00.399 --> 00:14:03.430
flaky. If you have a peace, you go with

00:14:03.440 --> 00:14:06.310
your peace, but there comes a

00:14:06.310 --> 00:14:06.320
point—there's

00:14:06.320 --> 00:14:08.310
wisdom behind

00:14:08.320 --> 00:14:10.870
everything we do. And God is a God of

00:14:10.880 --> 00:14:12.069
wisdom.

00:14:12.079 --> 00:14:13.990
And you say, 'Well, Brandon, I

00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:16.069
believe this.'I'm not

00:14:16.079 --> 00:14:17.350
trying to tell you to believe either

00:14:17.360 --> 00:14:19.350
way. I'm trying to tell you there's a

00:14:19.360 --> 00:14:22.230
balance of things. And I've seen

00:14:22.240 --> 00:14:27.030
both sides, and people get—when Megan was

00:14:27.040 --> 00:14:30.710
first diagnosed with autism,

00:14:30.720 --> 00:14:33.030
I was so scared because of the Word of

00:14:33.040 --> 00:14:34.710
Faith, of everybody saying you have what

00:14:34.720 --> 00:14:38.310
you say. Don't say that, because life

00:14:38.320 --> 00:14:39.750
and death is in the power of your

00:14:39.750 --> 00:14:39.760
tongue.

00:14:39.760 --> 00:14:42.550
Do you want that? And

00:14:42.560 --> 00:14:44.629
whenever I saw that

00:14:44.639 --> 00:14:46.470
she wasn't talking, I saw that things

00:14:46.480 --> 00:14:49.030
were going on with her and it was so

00:14:49.040 --> 00:14:51.670
bad, but I wouldn't allow other people

00:14:51.680 --> 00:14:54.389
to say the word 'autism.'In fact, if you

00:14:54.399 --> 00:14:56.150
said that word, I'd be ready to fight

00:14:58.000 --> 00:15:01.110
because I was scared of it. I was scared

00:15:01.120 --> 00:15:04.790
of the diagnosis of autism

00:15:04.800 --> 00:15:07.509
to the point where it was bondage. And

00:15:07.519 --> 00:15:11.030
even around her, we called it 'the

00:15:11.030 --> 00:15:11.040
A-word.'You

00:15:11.040 --> 00:15:12.870
know, 'the A-word, it looks like she

00:15:12.880 --> 00:15:14.550
might be...'It's flakiness, but that's where

00:15:14.560 --> 00:15:16.629
you get so much that you think, 'Well, I

00:15:16.639 --> 00:15:18.069
know that life and death is in the

00:15:18.079 --> 00:15:20.069
power of the tongue,'and I understand that

00:15:20.079 --> 00:15:22.710
you have what you say, you

00:15:22.720 --> 00:15:24.230
speak to the mountain, and you tell it to

00:15:24.240 --> 00:15:25.910
be removed and be cast into the sea,

00:15:25.910 --> 00:15:25.920
and

00:15:25.920 --> 00:15:27.350
if you don't doubt in your heart,

00:15:27.360 --> 00:15:28.949
you shall have whatsoever things you say.

00:15:28.959 --> 00:15:31.509
I believe that you are snared by the

00:15:31.519 --> 00:15:34.550
words of your mouth. I understand that.

00:15:34.560 --> 00:15:36.230
But there gets to be a point in time

00:15:36.240 --> 00:15:38.790
where you get flaky with stuff.

00:15:38.800 --> 00:15:42.710
And I'm not denying autism. I'm

00:15:42.720 --> 00:15:45.829
denying its right to be there.

00:15:45.839 --> 00:15:46.710
Yes,

00:15:46.720 --> 00:15:48.310
I'm denying its right to be there. I say

00:15:48.320 --> 00:15:50.230
it doesn't have a right to stay.

00:15:50.240 --> 00:15:52.470
I'm not denying the poor report

00:15:52.480 --> 00:15:54.790
of what all these

00:15:54.790 --> 00:15:54.800
neuropsychologists

00:15:54.800 --> 00:15:55.269
have said,

00:15:55.279 --> 00:15:56.310
because they're just doing their job,

00:15:57.839 --> 00:15:59.430
and all the

00:15:59.440 --> 00:15:59.749
therapists,

00:15:59.759 --> 00:16:01.509
and everybody who's ever tried to help

00:16:01.519 --> 00:16:02.629
us.

00:16:02.639 --> 00:16:04.949
At the beginning,

00:16:04.959 --> 00:16:06.310
we didn't want to

00:16:06.320 --> 00:16:08.069
do anything.

00:16:08.079 --> 00:16:09.430
But then the more we went to these

00:16:09.440 --> 00:16:10.629
