00:16:10.639 --> 00:16:11.990
helping us,

00:16:12.000 --> 00:16:13.990
you go, 'Well, is this

00:16:13.990 --> 00:16:14.000
God?'I

00:16:14.000 --> 00:16:16.470
was so grieved—I'm telling

00:16:16.480 --> 00:16:18.470
you all, this is a major deal

00:16:18.480 --> 00:16:20.629
because this is bondage. And I cried

00:16:20.639 --> 00:16:23.269
myself to sleep because of the diagnosis

00:16:23.279 --> 00:16:25.030
when the state people came into our house, and they

00:16:27.120 --> 00:16:29.110
evaluated her and

00:16:29.120 --> 00:16:31.030
they helped us, and they said, 'This is

00:16:31.040 --> 00:16:32.790
what she's going—what's the level that

00:16:32.800 --> 00:16:34.870
she's at,'and all the things. And when we

00:16:34.880 --> 00:16:36.790
went to the neuropsychologist, and

00:16:36.790 --> 00:16:36.800
the neuropsychologist

00:16:36.800 --> 00:16:39.030
told us, 'She'll be at

00:16:39.040 --> 00:16:40.629
this level for the rest of her

00:16:40.629 --> 00:16:40.639
life,'and

00:16:40.639 --> 00:16:42.150
all

00:16:42.160 --> 00:16:43.670
this death sentence is what you

00:16:43.680 --> 00:16:45.670
hear about a dream of what you had for

00:16:45.680 --> 00:16:47.350
your daughter,

00:16:47.360 --> 00:16:50.150
a marriage, a family,

00:16:50.160 --> 00:16:53.189
a job, everything that

00:16:53.199 --> 00:16:55.590
you ever wanted for her as a mom and a

00:16:55.600 --> 00:16:58.790
dad, to think that maybe one day, that

00:16:58.800 --> 00:17:01.430
moment of what that doctor was saying

00:17:01.440 --> 00:17:03.590
was basically a death sentence to

00:17:03.600 --> 00:17:06.069
those dreams.

00:17:06.079 --> 00:17:09.110
And at that time, that's all

00:17:09.120 --> 00:17:11.829
we could see. And in the midst, when

00:17:11.839 --> 00:17:13.429
you're that close to the

00:17:13.439 --> 00:17:15.110
trees and

00:17:15.120 --> 00:17:17.829
