you know how that's like a kick in the

00:17:31.679 --> 00:17:33.830
gut? Especially from people that you love,

00:17:33.840 --> 00:17:34.950
and they tell you that kind of stuff, and

00:17:34.960 --> 00:17:36.470
they're so

00:17:36.480 --> 00:17:37.909
