00:17:52.960 --> 00:17:54.870
Everybody's a work in

00:17:54.870 --> 00:17:54.880
progress.'I'll

00:17:54.880 --> 00:17:57.430
tell you how

00:17:57.440 --> 00:17:59.590
many times I had people say, 'Well, you must

00:17:59.590 --> 00:17:59.600
have

00:17:59.600 --> 00:18:01.590
