00:18:05.280 --> 00:18:07.669
that God's punishing you, and that all this

00:18:07.669 --> 00:18:07.679
happened?'And

00:18:07.679 --> 00:18:09.270
you know how many times

00:18:09.270 --> 00:18:09.280
I'd

00:18:09.280 --> 00:18:10.870
go home and just cry myself to sleep. I

00:18:10.870 --> 00:18:10.880
