00:18:20.559 --> 00:18:23.830
cry. That cost us our marriage. How many

00:18:23.840 --> 00:18:25.510
times did we say, 'I can't live

00:18:25.520 --> 00:18:27.350
this anymore. I have so much pressure on

00:18:27.360 --> 00:18:29.990
me. I've messed up

00:18:30.000 --> 00:18:32.549
