00:18:58.480 --> 00:19:01.350
visitation I had with the Lord. And

00:19:01.360 --> 00:19:04.470
He said, 'Whatever you do and you mess

00:19:04.480 --> 00:19:07.029
up on, Brandon, if you're upright with

00:19:07.039 --> 00:19:10.230
me and you're seeking me, you're not big

00:19:10.240 --> 00:19:13.110
enough to mess up your life.

00:19:13.120 --> 00:19:15.590
You're not big enough to mess up your

00:19:15.600 --> 00:19:18.150
life, Brandon. The footsteps of the

00:19:18.160 --> 00:19:20.390
righteous are ordered of the Lord. And no

00:19:20.400 --> 00:19:23.270
matter how bad you mess up, or if you

00:19:23.280 --> 00:19:24.870
