00:19:24.870 --> 00:19:24.880
derailed

00:19:24.880 --> 00:19:27.510
your life, I can turn it on a

00:19:27.520 --> 00:19:30.630
dime, son. No matter how bad the shots

00:19:30.640 --> 00:19:32.950
did this, or how bad this was with Megan

00:19:32.960 --> 00:19:35.669
